reviewText: Cant go wrong.  Love Miss Mass.  I listen to them all the time.  The songs are great and uplifting.
Nice video. I'd heard through the grapevine that this album was going to be sold as a CD/DVD set; obviously, I was wrong. Just goes to show you that you shouldn't believe everything you hear.
Love it look at it a lot sometimes. My favorite choir
Just what is expected from Mississippi Mass.
